#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:2
msgid "Model Context Protocol (MCP) — Ticket Server"
msgstr "模型上下文协议（MCP）——工单服务"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:5
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:7
msgid ""
"Loonflow exposes a **Model Context Protocol** server that lets compatible"
" clients (for example AI-assisted editors) query and handle tickets "
"through authenticated tools. The server name advertised to clients is "
"``loonflow-ticket``. Tools call the same permission-aware ticket services"
" as the web UI."
msgstr ""
"Loonflow 提供 **模型上下文协议（Model Context Protocol）** 服务端点，使兼容的客户端（例如带 AI "
"能力的编辑器）在通过认证后查询与处理工单。对客户端展示的服务名称为 ``loonflow-ticket``。工具内部调用与 Web "
"界面一致的、带权限校验的工单服务。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:10
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "认证方式"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:12
msgid ""
"Calls must be authenticated with an **access token**. Supported token "
"types include:"
msgstr "调用必须使用 **访问令牌（access token）** 进行认证。支持的令牌类型包括："

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:14
msgid ""
"**Personal access token** (recommended for MCP clients): values start "
"with ``lfpat.``"
msgstr "**个人访问令牌（Personal access token）**（推荐用于 MCP 客户端）：值以 ``lfpat.`` 开头"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:15
msgid "**JWT** issued by Loonflow (same as API usage)"
msgstr "由 Loonflow 签发的 **JWT**（与 API 用法相同）"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:17
msgid ""
"You can pass the token in the MCP HTTP client as a header (see "
"configuration below), pass it per tool where supported, or configure a "
"server-side environment variable for non-interactive setups."
msgstr "你可以在 MCP 的 HTTP 客户端中以请求头传递令牌（见下文配置）、在支持的工具参数中传入，或在无人值守场景下通过服务端环境变量配置。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:20
msgid "Create a personal access token"
msgstr "创建个人访问令牌"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:22
msgid ""
"Open **Personal Information** in the product UI, then open **Personal "
"Access Token**. Create a new token and store it securely. Replace ``xxx``"
" in the configuration example with that token."
msgstr ""
"在产品界面进入 **个人信息（Personal Information）**，再进入 **个人访问令牌（Personal Access "
"Token）**。新建令牌并妥善保存，将配置示例中的 ``xxx`` 替换为该令牌。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:25
msgid "Personal Information and Personal Access Token in Loonflow"
msgstr "Loonflow 中的个人信息与个人访问令牌"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:29
#, fuzzy
msgid "Navigate to Personal Information → Personal Access Token."
msgstr "Loonflow 中的个人信息与个人访问令牌"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:31
msgid "Create personal access token dialog or form"
msgstr "创建个人访问令牌的对话框或表单"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:35
#, fuzzy
msgid "Create or manage personal access tokens."
msgstr "创建个人访问令牌"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:38
msgid "Client configuration (example)"
msgstr "客户端配置（示例）"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:40
msgid ""
"Use the Streamable HTTP endpoint exposed by the MCP process (default path"
" ``/mcp``). Adjust host and port to match your deployment; local "
"development often uses port ``8002``."
msgstr ""
"使用 MCP 进程提供的 Streamable HTTP 端点（默认路径 ``/mcp``）。请按实际部署修改主机与端口；本地开发常见端口为 "
"``8002``。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:42
msgid ""
"For the Loonflow SaaS service, use ``https://mcp.loonflow.com/mcp`` as "
"the MCP server URL."
msgstr "对于 Loonflow SaaS 服务，请使用 ``https://mcp.loonflow.com/mcp`` 作为 MCP 服务地址。"

#: ../../source/mcp/index.rst:57
msgid ""
"Replace ``xxx`` with your **personal access token**. If the client "
"supports separate auth configuration, you may alternatively send ``X"
"-Loonflow-Access-Token`` with the raw token value."
msgstr ""
"将 ``xxx`` 替换为你的 **个人访问令牌**。若客户端支持单独配置认证信息，也可改用请求头 ``X-Loonflow-Access-"
"Token`` 传入原始令牌值。"

